; LC3 Machine Code
; Takes value in x3100
; Left Shifts the value by the shift amount stored in x3101
; Stores the result in x3102


; Begin Program at Memory Location x3000
0011 0000 0000 0000

; Step 0: Store Registers R0, R1 and R7
0011 000 000001101
0011 001 000001101
0011 111 000001101

; Step 1: Read into R0 from memory location x3100
0010 000 011111100

; Step 2: Read into R1 from memory location x3101
0010 001 011111100

; Step 3: When done, skip to step 6
0000 110 000000011

; Step 4: Add R0 to itself to left-shift once
0001 000 000 000 000

; Step 5: Update R1 and Return to step 3
0001 001 0 0 1111111
0100 1 11111111100

; Step 6: Store answer in x3102
0011 000 011111000

; Step 7: Restore R0, R1 and R7
0010 000 000000011
0010 001 000000011
0010 111 000000011

;Step 8a: Halt the Processor
;1111 0000 00100101

;Step 8b: Return From Subroutine
1100 000 111 000000